5273.html|title=Big Lots Appoints Two New Directors To Its Board After The Planned Retirement Of Existing Board Members|first=Big Lots|last=Inc|date=|website=prnewswire.com|accessdate=29 January 2019}}</ref>\n* [[David V. Miller]] \u2013 [[U.S. Air Force]] Major General<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.af.mil/About-Us/Biographies/Display/Article/106213/major-general-david-v-miller/|title=MAJOR GENERAL DAVID V. MILLER > U.S. Air Force > Biography Display|author=|date=|website=af.mil|accessdate=30 January 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Michael Mullen]], 1991 \u2013 [[Chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff]], United States armed forces<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.alumni.hbs.edu/stories/Pages/story-bulletin.aspx?num=867|title=At Ease - Alumni - Harvard Business School|author=|date=|website=alumni.hbs.edu|accessdate=2 February 2019}}</ref>\n* [[A. Sivathanu Pillai]], 1991 \u2013 honorary distinguished professor of [[Indian Space Research Organisation]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ishaeducation.org/insight/dr-sivathanu-pillai-ph-d-d-sc/|title=Dr. A. Sivathanu Pillai, Ph.D, D.Sc|author=|date=|website=ishaeducation.org|accessdate=29 January 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mechfisat.com/science-day-celebrations/|title=Celebrating Science and Scientists with Dr Sivathanu Pillai|author=|date=26 February 2018|website=mechfisat.com|accessdate=29 January 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Ajay Piramal]], 1992 \u2013 chairman, [[Piramal Group]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.alumni.hbs.edu/stories/Pages/story-bulletin.aspx?num=3367|title=Building a better India through business and philanthropy - Alumni - Harvard Business School|author=|date=|website=alumni.hbs.edu|accessdate=29 January 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Ratan Tata]], 1975 \u2013 chairman and CEO [[Tata Sons]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hbs.edu/about/campus-and-culture/campus-built-on-philanthropy/Pages/tata-hall.aspx|title=Tata Hall - About - Harvard Business School|author=|date=|website=hbs.edu|accessdate=29 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n=== Other ex