r their first meeting (1\u20130) but top 50 for their second meeting (1\u20130).|name=\"note1\"|group=\"nb\"}}\n*{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Mikhail Youzhny]] 2\u20130\n*{{flagicon|USA}} ''[[Jack Sock]]'' 2\u20130\n*{{flagicon|BUL}} ''[[Grigor Dimitrov]]'' 2\u20130\n*{{flagicon|CZE}} [[Luk\u00e1\u0161 Rosol]] 2\u20130\n*{{flagicon|ESP}} '''[[David Ferrer]]''' 2\u20130\n*{{flagicon|ITA}} ''[[Fabio Fognini]]'' 2\u20133\n*{{flagicon|CRO}} ''[[Ivo Karlovi\u0107]]'' 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|FRA}} ''[[Richard Gasquet]]'' 1\u20130 \n*{{flagicon|FRA}} ''[[J\u00e9r\u00e9my Chardy]]'' 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Borna \u0106ori\u0107]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Diego Schwartzman]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|UKR}} [[Sergiy Stakhovsky]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|USA}} [[Tim Smyczek]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|ISR}} [[Dudi Sela]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Pablo Carre\u00f1o Busta]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Facundo Arg\u00fcello (tennis)|Facundo Arguello]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|ITA}} ''[[Andreas Seppi]]'' 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Federico Delbonis]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Carlos Berlocq]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|CZE}} [[Ji\u0159\u00ed Vesel\u00fd]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Juan M\u00f3naco]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|NED}} [[Igor Sijsling]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|USA}} [[Donald Young (tennis)|Donald Young]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|FRA}} ''[[Gilles Simon]]'' 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Lucas Pouille]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|USA}} [[Steve Johnson (tennis)|Steve Johnson]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Simone Bolelli]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|TUR}} [[Marsel \u0130lhan]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Quentin Halys]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Andrey Kuznetsov (tennis)|Andrey Kuznetsov]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|CAN}} [[Vasek Pospisil]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|CHN}} [[Wu Di (tennis)|Wu Di]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|CYP}} [[Marcos Baghdatis]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|AUS}} ''[[Bernard Tomic]]'' 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|FRA}} ''[[Ga\u00ebl Monfils]]'' 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|SRB}} ''[[Viktor Troicki]]'' 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|DEN}} [[Mikael Torpegaard]] 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|CRO}} ''[[Marin \u010cili\u0107]]'' 1\u20130\n*{{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Andy Murray]]''' 1\u20131\n*{{flagicon|CZE}} '''[[Tom\u00e1\u0161 Berdych]]''' 1\u20131\n*{{flagicon|CAN}} '''[[Milos Raonic]]''' 1\u20131\n*{{flagicon|ESP}} ''[[Fernando Verdasco]]'' 1\u20131\n*{{flagicon|FRA}} ''[[Jo-Wilfried Tsonga]]'' 0\u20131\n*{{flagicon|ESP}} ''[[Feliciano L\u00f3pez]]'' 0\u20131\n*{{flagicon|GER}} [[Michael Berrer]] 0\u20131\n*{{flagicon|UKR}} [[Alexandr Dolgopolov]] 0\u20131\n*{{flagicon|GER}} [[Dustin Brown (tennis)|Dustin Brown]] 0\u20131\n*{{flagicon|JPN}} '''[[Kei Nishikori]]''' 0\u20131\n*{{flagicon|SWI}} '''[[Roger Federer]]''' 0\u20131\n*{{flagicon|SRB}} '''[[Novak Djokovic]]''' 0\u20134\n}}\n\n===Finals===\n\n====Singles: 6 (3\u20133)====\n{|\n|valign=top|\n{|class=wikitable\n!Category\n|-bgcolor=#f3e6d7\n|Grand Slam (0\u20130)\n|-bgcolor=ffffcc\n|ATP World Tour Finals (0\u20130)\n|-bgcolor=#e9e9e9\n|ATP World Tour Masters 1000 (0\u20131)\n|-bgcolor=#d4f1c5\n|ATP World Tour 500 (1\u20132)\n|-\n|ATP World Tour 250 (2\u20130)\n|}\n|valign=top|\n{|class=wikitable\n!Titles by Surface\n|-\n|Hard (0\u20132)\n|-\n|Clay (2\u20131)\n|-\n|Grass (1\u20130)\n|}\n|valign=top|\n{|class=wikitable\n!Titles by Location\n|-\n|Outdoors (3\u20132)\n|-\n|Indoors (0\u20131)\n|}\n|}\n\n{|class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n!Result\n!No.\n!Date\n!Category\n!Tournament\n!Surface\n!Opponent\n!Score\n|-\n|bgcolor=98fb98|Winner\n|65.\n|March 1, 2015\n|250 Series\n|[[ATP Buenos Aires|Argentina Open]], Buenos Aires, Argentina\n|Clay\n|{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Juan M\u00f3naco]]\n|6\u20134, 6\u20131\n|-\n|-bgcolor=#e9e9e9\n|bgcolor=FFA07A|Runner-up\n|29.\n|May 10, 2015\n|Masters 1000\n|[[Madrid Open (tennis)|Madrid Open]], Madrid, Spain\n|Clay\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Andy Murray]]\n|3\u20136, 2\u20136\n|-\n|bgcolor=98fb98|Winner\n|66.\n|June 14, 2015\n|250 Series\n|[[Stuttgart Open]], Stuttgart, Germany\n|Grass\n|{{flagicon|SRB}} [[Viktor